title: North vs South divide in Rugby World Cup quarterfinals
text:
> Sports North vs South divide in Rugby World Cup quarterfinals South Africa's Bryan Habana, right, and Tendai Mtawarira attend a training session at Pennyhill Park, in Bagshot, outside London, Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015. South Africa will play Wales during their Rugby World Cup quarterfinal match on Saturday, Oct. 17. (AP Photo/Christophe Ena) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
